**Dungeon Quest**

***DESCRIPTION***

DQ Version 1.4.4.4

Added support for Set top Boxes as well as Google TV Support!
As featured in TegraZone!
Optimized game play for NVIDIA Tegra Devices.
Play it on NVIDIA Shield - Complete SHIELD support and control integration added

Fixed a few HID Controller bugs.
Controller support has been enhanced for better game flow.

Addressed a few loading issues users reported.
PLEASE NOTE - The game will take longer to start up the FIRST TIME you play this patch. Gameplay should be much smoother on several devices.

Thank you to all of our players and community members for your support while we created this update.

If you need help or have questions:
